This flavourful prawn tikka masala recipe is the perfect and wholesome midweek dish to enjoy and can be prepared in under 30 minutes.  If you are not a fan of basmati rice then you can enjoy this dish over a bed of your favourite rice.  To make this a complete Indian feast, you can enjoy this prawn tikka masala and rice dish with either homemade or store-bought naan bread.  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Curried mutton pie This recipe was found on bbcgoodfood.com